text: @Apple Life was so much better when you shipped thru FedEx. @UPSHelp is the worst. They say my package which is due today has been rescheduled with no available date and the best they can do is to tell me to keep checking online.
@apple @UPSHelp It was supposed to be here today, so why is it still in China? 15 minutes on hold with no answers. #whereismypackage https://t.co/hJS0mASSO4

@bricat I understand your concerns regarding the delivery of the package. China was on Holiday from 09/22/18-09/24/18. The package is in transit and the delivery date will update soon. Please continue to track the package at https://t.co/d2jLd213F2 for updated info. ^SB
@UPSHelp It supposedly was leaving China on 9/21 according to my tracking page. Are you telling me that @ups misreports tracking info?

@ups @UPSHelp 3 different people talked to with 3 very different answers. The last being “no one can ever give you a scheduled date for an international delivery until it reaches the US”.  What a load of crap! Tell your employees to stop making up lies. @apple Please use @FedEx!
